My entry for the LHC mapping competition, It's not nearly as compleete as I would have liked, and is not really playable (multiplayer) as its only a small section baised on the superconducting magnets at the LHC and only has one spawn for testing.

I kind of rushed this and dont really expect to win anything but It's something. 

If anyone has any problems with the custom texture (although I forgot how to make it shiney), just contact me and I will try fix and re-upload.
